@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mdncgr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.58
    v0 = v0
    tmp = (0.31 * v0)
    v1 = (0.52 - wp.exp((v0 + 0.88 * v1 + 0.95)))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.sin(0.42))
    tmp = (tmp + (wp.abs(v2 + 0.10) * (v1 + 0.23 / v1 + 0.37)))
    tmp = v2
    data[tid] = v0
